        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-8">
          <div class="panel panel-primary">
           <div class="panel-heading">
            <h3 class="panel-title">About News</h3>
           </div>
           <div class="panel-body">
             NUTV News specializes in video coverage of occurrences on campus and across the city of Boston.
             We aim to shed light on issues that directly impact students, as well as provide nonfiction entertainment to our viewers.
             Check out some of our videos to learn more about what's going on around you!
           </div>
         </div>
      </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="panel panel-danger">
           <div class="panel-heading">
            <h3 class="panel-title"><i>Meetings</i></h3>
           </div>
           <div class="panel-body">
            <p>
              <b>When:</b> <br>
              Mondays <br>
              232 Curry - 7pm <br>
              <br>
              <b>Director:</b> <br>
                Scott Adelberg
              </p>
